title: Heartbeat 1946 (American Romantic Comedy film) Ginger Rogers, Jean-Pierre Aumont

sources.title: Heartbeat 1946 (American Romantic Comedy film) Ginger Rogers, Jean-Pierre Aumont
sources.description:
A daring, exciting adventure... in the world's most exciting capital!
In Paris, a young woman runs away from a reform school, joins a pickpocket academy, and finds herself falling for the handsome diplomat she's been blackmailed into stealing from.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/k_SHyCr9opk


Original title: Heartbeat (1946)
This film is available with English & Spanish audio, and also subtitled in many languages.


Director: Sam Wood
Writers: Morrie Ryskind, Hans Wilhelm 
Stars: Ginger Rogers, Jean-Pierre Aumont, Adolphe Menjou & Basil Rathbone
Genres: Classics, Drama, Comedy, Romance
